{"comments":"Canvas Render Layers — Main canvas rendering and layer composition.\n\n## Purpose\n\nProvides the main canvas render function and layer composition:\n- Main canvas render (composes all layers)\n- Background layer\n- Grid layer\n- Objects layer\n- Guides layer\n- Selection layer\n- Rulers layer\n\n## Render Structure\n\n```\n.canvas-container\n  .canvas-background\n  .canvas-grid-layer\n  .canvas-objects-layer\n  .canvas-guides-layer\n  .canvas-selection-layer\n  .canvas-rulers\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Canvas.State (CanvasState)\n- Canvas.Types (GridConfig, Guide)\n- Canvas.Selection (SelectionFrame, computeSelectionFrame)\n- Render.Types (RenderConfig, CanvasMsg)\n- Render.Helpers (sortByZIndex, viewportTransform)\n- Render submodules (Objects, Selection, Grid, Guides, Rulers)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render the canvas with default configuration.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","State","Core"],"CanvasState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Render","Types"],"CanvasMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,51],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Render/Layers.purs","start":[96,1]},"title":"canvas"},{"children":[],"comments":"Render the canvas with custom configuration.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Render","Types"],"Rend